    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Key Pieces of the Malbon Outdoors Club Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Malbon Outdoors Club Collection is defined by a curated selection of pieces that are versatile, stylish, and built for resilience. Each item in this F/W 2024 line seamlessly combines modern outdoor functionality with Malbon's iconic golfing aesthetic, making it easy to transition from the course to a weekend trek through the British countryside.</p><h4></h4><h4><strong>Bowman Fishing Jacket: Where Function Meets Style</strong></h4><p>The <strong>Malbon Bowman Fishing Jacket in Ivory</strong> is the standout piece for those who crave both utility and sophistication. Crafted from durable cotton twill, this jacket is designed to endure. Featuring snap-button closures, ample pocket space, and a classic collar, the Bowman exudes a sense of timeless ruggedness. Its neutral ivory shade is as versatile as it is fashionable, allowing it to blend effortlessly with the collection's earth-toned palette or to stand alone as a statement piece.</p><p>Whether you're layering up for a chilly day on the course or need reliable protection on a damp walk, the Bowman Fishing Jacket brings a fresh perspective to outdoor apparel. It's not just for the avid fisher\u2014it's for anyone who values functionality without compromising style.</p><h4><strong>Outerwear Essentials: From the Trail to the Tee</strong></h4><p>The collection's outerwear line goes beyond the Bowman Fishing Jacket, including various options that meet the demands of the British winter. Jackets are constructed to handle all-weather situations, featuring insulated fabrics, wind-resistant layers, and water-repellent finishes. Each piece is thoughtfully designed to ensure warmth and comfort in colder temperatures, making it a perfect addition to any wardrobe that sees frequent outdoor activity.</p><h4><strong>Accessories to Elevate Every Look</strong></h4><p>No collection is complete without accessories, and the Malbon Outdoors Club line doesn't disappoint. <strong>Caps and beanies </strong>make practical yet stylish additions, perfect for completing your ensemble. The earthy tones of the beanies and the subtle logo detailing on the caps add a sense of understated luxury, while scarves offer warmth without adding unnecessary bulk. Each piece is crafted to bring together functionality and style, keeping you comfortable and looking refined, whether you're hitting the course or taking a winter hike.</p>"
          }
        }
