        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Malbon has integrated eco-conscious practices into its production, selecting materials that are not only durable but also chosen with environmental impact in mind. While outdoor wear must be resilient, it's also increasingly important that brands consider their environmental footprint. The Outdoors Club Collection highlights this commitment by focusing on sustainable materials and production techniques that align with Malbon's ethos of quality and environmental respect.</p>"
