        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Malbon Golf Outdoors Club Collection is more than just a seasonal line; it's an invitation to embrace the outdoors in comfort, style, and sophistication. This collection allows fans of both Malbon and TRENDYGOLF to experience the best of outdoor and golf fashion, brought together in a cohesive, inspired collection. Whether you're an avid golfer, a weekend explorer, or simply someone with a deep appreciation for quality apparel, the Outdoors Club Collection offers pieces that are built to last, as beautiful as they are functional and perfectly suited to the British outdoor lifestyle.</p><p>With thoughtful design, earth-inspired colours, and functional features, Malbon has created a collection that serves both style-conscious urbanites and rugged outdoor enthusiasts alike. Embrace the outdoors with Malbon - no matter the weather, no matter the season.</p>"
          }
